## Section E: Integration Points
Harnesses and other domains should interact with the runtime via `ResolverChain.resolve(prompt_id, manifest)` and `resolve(prompt_id, ref_context=None, variables=None)`.
`runner.py` executes BYO harness adapters and strictly validates output artifacts against CONTRACT schemas.
